  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join Our Discord Community</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819190/extras/5f2fbc39d3d7e14e5e9e44f05c209b6e.avif?t=1758797510\" width=644 height=186 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >UNDEAD CITADEL hurls you into a relentless adventure, where you’ll face off against hundreds of undead in brutal, cinematic combat. Slash, stab, crush, shoot, or dismember with your own hands as you carve your path into the heart of the cursed citadel.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819190/extras/af4b4ca31a13cbef8e84684b46de36c6.poster.avif?t=1758797510\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819190/extras/af4b4ca31a13cbef8e84684b46de36c6.webm?t=1758797510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819190/extras/af4b4ca31a13cbef8e84684b46de36c6.mp4?t=1758797510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🗡️<strong>Physics-based Combat System</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Fight realistically using a complete physics system built specifically for VR. Swing, stab, block, and parry with 1:1 motion. Your weapons react naturally to force and timing, making every strike feel real and satisfying. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⚔️ <strong>Wide Arsenal of Weapons</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from over 60 weapons, including swords, axes, war hammers, bows, arrows, shields, two-handed weapons, and more. Use bombs, flasks, and even dismembered limbs to survive. Each weapon has its own stats for durability and strength.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819190/extras/11db2374823d6ec41f4008eb337ae4e5.poster.avif?t=1758797510\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819190/extras/11db2374823d6ec41f4008eb337ae4e5.webm?t=1758797510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819190/extras/11db2374823d6ec41f4008eb337ae4e5.mp4?t=1758797510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>💀Dozens of Unique Undead Foes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face a relentless horde of enemies in varying states of decay, each with distinct weapons, armor, and attack styles. Read their defenses, dodge or parry their blows, and strike with precision to exploit their weaknesses. And when they fall? Loot their weapons; they won’t need them anymore, but you definitely will.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819190/extras/dc7582f0d8707bbad23ced907e84020c.poster.avif?t=1758797510\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819190/extras/dc7582f0d8707bbad23ced907e84020c.webm?t=1758797510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819190/extras/dc7582f0d8707bbad23ced907e84020c.mp4?t=1758797510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎯<strong>Story Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover the dark secret behind the plague as you explore over 10 different environments. Engage in combat, solve puzzles, and experience a gripping narrative-driven journey through the depths of the Citadel.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔥 <strong>Horde Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight off endless waves of the undead and climb the online leaderboards. Test your skills and push your reflexes in pure survival chaos.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🛡️ <strong>Armory Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Freely test all unlocked weapons, potions, and items in a safe sandbox to practice your moves and combos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819190/extras/7de78401fc02273cbf68b9c26ad7041a.poster.avif?t=1758797510\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819190/extras/7de78401fc02273cbf68b9c26ad7041a.webm?t=1758797510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819190/extras/7de78401fc02273cbf68b9c26ad7041a.mp4?t=1758797510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🏃‍♂️LOCOMOTION</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Various options for moving around with smooth and instant turning via smooth locomotion.</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ready to test your mettle and face the horrors within, <strong>Warrior</strong>? <br> <br>Sharpen your blade, steady your aim, and prepare to enter the Undead Citadel.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >UNDEAD CITADEL hurls you into a relentless adventure, where you’ll face off against hundreds of undead in brutal, cinematic combat. Slash, stab, crush, shoot, or dismember with your own hands as you carve your path into the heart of the cursed citadel.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819190/extras/af4b4ca31a13cbef8e84684b46de36c6.poster.avif?t=1758797510\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819190/extras/af4b4ca31a13cbef8e84684b46de36c6.webm?t=1758797510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819190/extras/af4b4ca31a13cbef8e84684b46de36c6.mp4?t=1758797510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🗡️<strong>Physics-based Combat System</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Fight realistically using a complete physics system built specifically for VR. Swing, stab, block, and parry with 1:1 motion. Your weapons react naturally to force and timing, making every strike feel real and satisfying. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⚔️ <strong>Wide Arsenal of Weapons</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from over 60 weapons, including swords, axes, war hammers, bows, arrows, shields, two-handed weapons, and more. Use bombs, flasks, and even dismembered limbs to survive. Each weapon has its own stats for durability and strength.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819190/extras/11db2374823d6ec41f4008eb337ae4e5.poster.avif?t=1758797510\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819190/extras/11db2374823d6ec41f4008eb337ae4e5.webm?t=1758797510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819190/extras/11db2374823d6ec41f4008eb337ae4e5.mp4?t=1758797510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>💀Dozens of Unique Undead Foes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face a relentless horde of enemies in varying states of decay, each with distinct weapons, armor, and attack styles. Read their defenses, dodge or parry their blows, and strike with precision to exploit their weaknesses. And when they fall? Loot their weapons; they won’t need them anymore, but you definitely will.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819190/extras/dc7582f0d8707bbad23ced907e84020c.poster.avif?t=1758797510\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819190/extras/dc7582f0d8707bbad23ced907e84020c.webm?t=1758797510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819190/extras/dc7582f0d8707bbad23ced907e84020c.mp4?t=1758797510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎯<strong>Story Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover the dark secret behind the plague as you explore over 10 different environments. Engage in combat, solve puzzles, and experience a gripping narrative-driven journey through the depths of the Citadel.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔥 <strong>Horde Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight off endless waves of the undead and climb the online leaderboards. Test your skills and push your reflexes in pure survival chaos.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🛡️ <strong>Armory Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Freely test all unlocked weapons, potions, and items in a safe sandbox to practice your moves and combos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819190/extras/7de78401fc02273cbf68b9c26ad7041a.poster.avif?t=1758797510\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819190/extras/7de78401fc02273cbf68b9c26ad7041a.webm?t=1758797510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819190/extras/7de78401fc02273cbf68b9c26ad7041a.mp4?t=1758797510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🏃‍♂️LOCOMOTION</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Various options for moving around with smooth and instant turning via smooth locomotion.</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ready to test your mettle and face the horrors within, <strong>Warrior</strong>? <br> <br>Sharpen your blade, steady your aim, and prepare to enter the Undead Citadel.</p>",
